So we're going to be working
in keyframe animations, and

3
00:00:06.937 --> 00:00:09.063
that's at 0 to dash keyframes.

4
00:00:09.063 --> 00:00:13.287
What we want to do is add animations for
this entering in, so

5
00:00:13.287 --> 00:00:17.606
we want the form to sort of slide up or
whatever you want to do.

6
00:00:17.606 --> 00:00:21.362
But I think that that's a good
intro to just getting a feel for

7
00:00:21.362 --> 00:00:22.843
in meeting something.

8
00:00:22.843 --> 00:00:26.659
And we might also want
to add animation for

9
00:00:26.659 --> 00:00:31.029
each of the elements as
well when they enter in.

10
00:00:31.029 --> 00:00:34.903
So this would just be an animation
that you add directly to the elements.

11
00:00:34.903 --> 00:00:36.421
And when you load the page,

12
00:00:36.421 --> 00:00:39.525
those animations are going
to be immediately applied.

13
00:00:39.525 --> 00:00:43.625
And so
the final thing I want you to do is to

14
