15
00:00:48.099 --> 00:00:51.549
And we're going to be using
that in a later exercise.

16
00:00:51.549 --> 00:00:56.018
But shaking is just you're
transforming from a native translate X

17
00:00:56.018 --> 00:00:58.982
to a positive translate X, back and forth.

18
00:00:58.982 --> 00:01:03.357
So you could use some of the shorthand
techniques that we learned in order to

19
00:01:03.357 --> 00:01:04.890
